summary: Email correspondence between individuals discussing a draft application for an amended search warrant to correct FBI barcode numbers for three devices seized from Jeffrey Epstein's New York residence. The email includes attachments of the draft application and referenced exhibits.

events.title: Draft Application for Amended Search Warrant
events.description: Email correspondence regarding a draft application for an amended search warrant to correct FBI barcode numbers for three devices seized from Jeffrey Epstein's New York residence.

keyFacts: The document is an email dated October 22, 2020, regarding an amended search warrant application.
The amendment seeks to correct FBI barcode numbers for three devices seized from Jeffrey Epstein's New York residence.
Attachments include a draft application and referenced exhibits.
The correspondence indicates ongoing legal or investigative procedures related to evidence from Epstein's residence.
